            <lg xml:id="TK25">
<l>aintavittā ṉāṟṟa lakalvicumpu ḷārkōmā</l>
<l>ṉintiraṉē cāluṅ kari</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For the might of one who cut off the five cravings, the king of those</l>
<l>who dwell in wide Heaven—Indra himself—is fitting witness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
